==Dutch==

===Verb===
'''horen'''
# To [[hear]].
#: ''Iets leuks horen.'' &mdash; To hear something nice.
# To [[belong]]; [[should]] (be).
#: ''Dat hoort hier te liggen.'' &mdash; That belongs (to be lying) here; that should be lying here.
#: ''Je hoort dat zo te doen.'' &mdash; You should do it that way.

